title: Witchcraft Adult Manga
description:
Witchcraft is a story about a boy whose life has reached bottom, he's always bullied by older boys, he alse has the look of a nerd. However everything changes when he walks inside a fortune teller's house and accepts to be the "assistant" of a beautiful fortune teller chick.

The twist is that she is studying the art of hypnosis, and realizes that during being hypnotized he transforms literally in a sex machine, who can last for hours before he gets tired.

Its an interesting story, with pretty good drawing and nice women characters. It's not the usual big tits, lots of sperm and huge dicks, worth a try.

And yes its clean from viruses, trojans, bla bla bla bla.

Enjoy.
